I"´@<h1 id="san-miguel-del-vado-historic-district">San Miguel del Vado Historic District</h1>

<figure class="img-center" style="width:66%">
  <a class="image" href="
    /sites/images/san-migel-del-vado-1846.jpg
  "><img src="
    /sites/images/san-migel-del-vado-1846.jpg
